contentrichtext.text: '''Chem''' may refer to: *[[Chemistry]] *Post apocalyptic slang for "drugs", medicinal or otherwise in the [[Fallout (video game)|Fallout]] video game series. In Ancient Egyptian usage: *[[Kemet (disambiguation)#History of the Word|''Khem'']] (also spelt ''Chem''), the Egyptian word for "black" *[[Min (god)]], in the past erroneously named ''Khem'' '''CHEM''' may refer to : *A [[metabolic panel (disambiguation)|metabolic panel]]: for instance, CHEM-7, which is the [[basic metabolic panel]] *[[CHEM-TV]], a Canadian television channel ==See also== *[[Kemi]], a place in Finland {{disambig}}
